    "video_prompt": "A young penguin man listens intently to his blue hedgehog friend, a gentle, warm smile spreading across his beak. He nods slowly in agreement while holding a large watermelon, his fingers idly tracing its smooth surface. The camera films from over the shoulder of the speaking hedgehog, gently swaying with the easy, relaxed rhythm of their conversation, capturing the penguin's focused eyes and relaxed posture."
