    "video_prompt": "A young penguin man powerfully splits a large watermelon in half with his bare hands, revealing the vibrant red flesh inside. With focused eyes and a steady hand, he pours fresh juice into two tall glasses. He then extends one glass toward the blue hedgehog boy. The camera gently tracks the entire sequence, smoothly following the watermelon splitting, the pouring motion, and the hand-off of the glass. The hedgehog boy receives the glass with both hands, his lips curving into a grateful smile as he nods."
